headline: Idex (IEX) Soars 7.3%: Is Further Upside Left in the Stock?
summary: Idex (IEX) witnessed a jump in share price last session on above-average trading volume. The latest trend in earnings estimate revisions for the stock doesn't suggest further strength down the road.
